			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Pets: <BR>
Don't forget that if you go invisible now, your pet will become very panicky and hit itself for 32000 points of damage, committing suicide. So you can't go invis with your invis air pet.<BR>
<BR>
Fights:<BR>
When fighting more than one creature with a group, try to get the group to lure the creatures to one position. Then you can use AE (area effect) spells to their best. Column of fire usually does between 30 and 60 damage to all the creatures that are stood within its area of effect.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
